lead_paragraph: Ashton Eaton and Brianne Theisen-Eaton, athletics' best-known couple, are not letting widespread concerns about the Zika virus stand in the way of a bid for unprecedented double gold medals at the Rio Olympics.

headline.print_headline: Eatons Looking for Unprecedented Double Gold in Rio
